==Profit analysis==
Considering the Grand Exchange values and probabilities of obtaining each staff, repairing a Broken staff will on average yield {{Coins|floor (0.57*{{GEP|Staff}} + 0.26*{{GEP|Magic staff}} + 0.05*{{GEP|Staff of water}} + 0.04*{{GEP|Staff of fire}} + 0.04*{{GEP|Staff of air}} + 0.04*{{GEP|Staff of earth}}) }}. Thus repairing broken staves is hardly worth it even in bulk.

